## Advanced Operating Systems
<hr />
<br />

### Instructor(s)

[Sid Touati](http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Sid.Touati/)

### Description

* 2 ECTS

*Objectives*

This course is devoted to master students willing to understand the
kernel of an operating system. While this course is not devoted to a
special operating system, we however provide some technical examples
with linux and windows.
The course describes some advanced topics on operating systems:  threads
and process, scheduling, file systems and virtual memory.
Laboratory classes are organised under linux environment.

### Prerequisites

* Knowledge of an operating system (programming, shell)

